panels.description: An average gauge of the JVM's non-heap memory usage across coordinators.

targets.expr: avg (jvm_nonheap_memory_used{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance", presto_cluster=~"$presto_cluster"} / clamp_min((jvm_nonheap_memory_used{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance", presto_cluster=~"$presto_cluster"} + jvm_nonheap_memory_committed{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance", presto_cluster=~"$presto_cluster"}),1))

panels.title: Non-heap memory usage

panels.description: An average gauge of the JVM's heap memory usage across coordinators.

targets.expr: avg (jvm_heap_memory_used{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance", presto_cluster=~"$presto_cluster"} / clamp_min((jvm_heap_memory_used{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance", presto_cluster=~"$presto_cluster"} + jvm_heap_memory_committed{job=~"$job", instance=~"$instance", presto_cluster=~"$presto_cluster"}),1))
